--------------------
About LUSI
--------------------

LUSI (Library for Sourcecode Install) is a library to install/uninstall/update
sourcecode packages. The intention is automatize as much as possible the
configure/build/install routine and future uninstallations or updates.

It is licensed under the GNU GPL license. It is also free as in "free beer".
See COPYING file for license.



--------------------
Installing LUSI
--------------------

See INSTALL file instead.



